4:["$","p","1",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base","children":"We use progressive balance exercises on stable and unstable surfaces, combining visual and head movements. This re-trains the brain to process spatial orientation."}]
5:["$","p","2",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base","children":"Gait analysis allows us to correct stepping symmetry and weight shifting. Correcting these patterns builds confidence and reduces the risk of falls."}]
